item.title: Graduation and New Member, 2025
item.description: HyungJun received his Master’s degree and graduated this winter! Big congratulations! We are very proud of you. Also ASML got new member in the winter, 2025. Jieun, we welcome you!

item.title: Graduation, 2024 winter
item.description: Kyunghun Han earned the Master’s degree and graduated in February, 2024! He returned to the navy and continued to serve as a naval officer. Big congratulations! We are very proud of you. ~

item.title: Graduation, 2023 summer
item.description: Chaehyeong received his Master’s degree and graduated this summer! Also SeungYeon received her Bachelor’s degree and graduated this summer! Big congratulations! We are very proud of you.

item.title: Graduation and New Member,2023
item.description: Yujin and Hyojun received their Master’s degree and graduated this winter! Big congratulations! We are very proud of you. They joined ASML as doctoral students and will be with us for another few more years. Also, ASML got new member in the winter, 2023. Hyungjun, we welcome you!
